      "title": "#OccupyGalleFace continues",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Occupy Galle Face Protest or known as #GotaGoGama in front of the President\u2019s office continues today for the 104th day.",
        "The peaceful protesters demanded that the current Government including the new President Ranil Wickramasinghe with NO mandate should resign.",
        "The people who came to the protest site last night also engaged in various activities."
      ],
